{{Top|leg}}
The '''Blood Velkers''' were a gang active on [[Genarius]], on the floating [[City/Legends|cities]] of [[Tolea Biqua]] and [[Varna Biqua]]. As with most gangs of young toughs, they spent their time amusing themselves and causing trouble. As a right of initiation, the Blood Velkers would race through the tunnels of [[Eskaron]].<ref name="Living Force Campaign Guide">''[[Living Force Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The Blood Velkers were first mentioned in the ''[[Living Force Campaign Guide]]''. They were later called the "Blood Velkurs" in two supplementary articles. The spelling "Velker" is preferred as it is the earlier spelling and corresponds to the [[Velker/Legends|Velkers]] of [[Bespin/Legends|Bespin]], a flying creature.

